        <Parent_String>sports buildings by form [300007254], sports buildings [300007250], recreation buildings [300007193], recreation structures [300122263], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
